**[^2]Example 6.16:** For the configurations in Fig. 6.34(a), determine the small-signal resistances $R_{X}$ and $R_{Y}$. Assume $\lambda \neq 0$.

**Figure 6.34 (a):** Diode-connected NMOS and PMOS devices, (b) small-signal model of (a), (c) small-signal model of (b).

**Solution:** For the NMOS version, the small-signal equivalent is as shown in Fig. 6.34(b), resulting in

$$
\begin{align*}
