**Example:** In the circuit shown in Fig. 6.33, determine the operational region of $M_{1}$ as $V_{1}$ varies from $V_{D D}$ (2.5 V) to zero, assuming $\left|V_{T H}\right|=0.5 \mathrm{~V}$.

**Figure 6.33:** Simple PMOS circuit.

